Revision history for Perl extension SMS::Send::Adapter::Node::Red.

0.09 2024-12-29
  - Added default driver from INI file
  - Switched from JSON to JSON::XS

0.08 2023-12-20
  - Updated lib/SMS/Send/Adapter/Node/Red.pm to allow default Driver from environment SMS_SEND_ADAPTER_NODE_RED_DRIVER

0.07 2021-03-28
  - Updated SMS::Send::Adapter::Node::Red to added PSGI capability
