    - Added scripts/perl-SMS-Send-Adapter-Node-Red.psgi example script
    - Added scripts/perl-SMS-Send-Adapter-Node-Red-plack-builder.psgi example script
  - Updated t/001_load.t added test coverage
  - Updated perl-SMS-Send-Adapter-Node-Red.spec to install PSGI scripts
  
